For the templates that display text in a colored box.

== 使用方法 ==
<CODE><nowiki>{{</nowiki>color box|''color''|''text''|''text color''<nowiki>}}</nowiki></CODE>

*Colors are most commonly specified as either a color keyword or as the hexadecimal triplet representing an RGB combination.  See [[网页颜色模式|web colors]] for details.
*If specified, the <CODE>text</CODE> is centered within the box.
*If no color is specified for the text, it is displayed using the default style foreground color as prescribed by [[Cascading Style Sheets|CSS]]. For most users this is black.

